            "type": "TextualBody",
            "value": "I really like how the language looks like a bunch of squiggles and symbols. I think it is really representative of what language looks and sounds like to someone who has no background in the structure of the language and its alphabet. Making the writing look like this really puts us in the shoes of an immigrant because, like the protagonist, we know as much as he does about the new world that he is in.",
